{"tid":445832,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"1月去北海道，買mont-bell羽絨定superdry好？","createTime":"2017-10-23T17:35:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-11T07:01:40.000Z","uid":51345,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"a7613e3c2f27bfe8603da1e1b0f1878eadbf6487","tid":445832,"uid":51345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T17:35:39.000Z","msg":"唔會滑雪，唔洗用到雪衣咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSuperdry有件個款幾靚，但佢係棉襖，唔係羽絨 （上佢官網online shop搵唔到圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\nMontbell就係羽絨，但個款冇superdry咁好睇<br />\n價錢就兩件都啱budget<br />\nMontbell個款係咁：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/24/012930_4ef77c245c58ae8b6bd4390d7196fee8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F24%2F012930_4ef77c245c58ae8b6bd4390d7196fee8.jpg&h=c3f0a8c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底買邊件好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n棉襖去北海道夠唔夠暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb272f65254f0ca16cfbda7eea3b7aa2cbf8fbf5","tid":445832,"uid":51345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T17:41:26.000Z","msg":"唔係棉襖 係夾棉先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d83db4a2876847398e82f275eb194670a372481","tid":445832,"uid":51345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T17:45:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35ec128fc18d154d96c12c7389a0b2d3c155de44","tid":445832,"uid":13882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T17:47:17.000Z","msg":"去北海道咁凍，羽絨會暖d<br />\n但係就要拎去乾洗<br />\nbtw最好出面加件gtx防風防水褸"},{"pid":"11325bcdbfda0a40063f5857c2f542f090adec99","tid":4