,"msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你budget 係幾多？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBudget 2000內<br />\n如果件羽絨本身話防風防水仲洗唔洗要多件gtx喺出面？</blockquote><br />\nMontbell 件1101502 防風但太薄 要加保暖內衣，但係夠輕好爽</blockquote><br />\n巴打有着過？<br />\n我就係貪佢夠輕 可以方便帶去旅行<br />\n保暖內衣有冇推薦？</blockquote><br />\n1101502 防風 外面唔需要再加gtx, 內衣odlo montbell ,odlo太厚 montbell 最厚羊毛比較貴</blockquote><br />\n雞仔嘜內衣巴打覺得點？</blockquote><br />\n未著過，話哂戶外界 好多有研究測試，功能性強好多，D人的去雪山都搵專業戶外牌子</blockquote><br />\n咁我去montbell順便睇埋啲內衣先～唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bca8e6a9cca1ebf54ea2df140703cd8a68dbfadb","tid":445832,"uid":51345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T18:28:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一月中去京都1000蚊budget買邊件好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無人推介下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我上年一月喺大阪同京都都係着啲劣劣地嘅淘寶羽絨<br />\n勉強夠暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432a7fb189af5ed21e68d28e7c81c8990b3dbdf6","tid":445832,"uid":51345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T18:29:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己著開 AIGLE d打底衫 好掂<br />\n暖得黎又唔覺得焗身</blockquote><br />\n大約幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"2c75a56391f1f95cadf6e10be32ae4a9db5f55ef","tid":445832,"uid":13882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T18:31:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>要分清楚 Water repellent 定waterproof<br />\n防潑水同防水唔同</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來係咁<br />\n巴打有冇推介？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自己去落雪個d地方就著一件保暖打底衫<br />\n之後一件衛衣或者長䄂T<br />\n中層就著羽絨或者纖維褸<br />\n面頭再加件gtx<br />\n貪佢防風防水<br />\n如果就咁羽絨，因為會入風 所以硬係覺得無咁暖<br />\n<br />\n有時候去滑雪場因為大風雪所以有件防水褸都方便好多，個身一定唔會濕但如果你只係去啲會落少少雪嘅地方你防潑水都可以嘅，不過最好擔返把遮"},{"pid":"23f1883737fa42194ad47a2db210f6eff2be14b4","tid":445832,"uid":13882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T18:32:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自己著開 AIGLE d打底衫 好掂<br />\n暖得黎又唔覺得焗身</blockquote><br />\n大約幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n大約500蚊一件，自己都著左7年"},{"pid":"021aefb1da16da7b5e6c323f8e030c35ab3678b8","tid":445832,"uid":45261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T18:32:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一月中去京都1000蚊budget買邊件好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無人推介下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我上年一月喺大阪同京都都係着啲劣劣地嘅淘寶羽絨<br />\n勉強夠暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上年一月我著Alpha Ma1 直頭熱（入面一件薄長袖）"},{"pid":"d37cd2699399668ea8c4f2639c36069539f982db","tid":445832,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T18:34:16.000Z","msg":"2000內應該唔夠啦，直接買件gtx連內膽5千應該ok"},{"pid":"f334e401ef11e579adb956e85ede161bebfd33ef","tid":445832,"uid":80461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T18:34:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>求其買件Montbell啦 再打下底<br />\n唔好企足幾個鐘街就乜都差唔多</blockquote><br />\n見啲人着過都話montbell唔錯～<br />\n咁褲呢？洗唔洗着條legging打底？定係加絨褲就夠？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n褲就一定要打底啦，唔洗講<br />\n同埋睇下你去邊啦最主要<br />\n行市內多既就著厚少少就ok la <br />\n第一次去我諗都唔會走得去邊啦，最多咪小樽左右"},{"pid":"94b085dcf5e05295d7f0e5b1d65479d8ad18c294","tid":445832,"uid":106614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T18:37:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>columbia</blockquote><br />\n我見啲人話columbia唔保暖 巴打有冇着過？覺得點？</blockquote><br />\n兩件款外面gore tex入面羽絨銀底果種<br />\n其實都好暖<br />\n唔夠加多件super warm/雞仔嘜</blockquote><br />\n聽日去睇下先<br />\n唔該巴打～</blockquote><br />\n之前行山用過 4度 身夠暖 個頭就好凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27a7aabb35ba1aeea9f77cb38bfb21185bdac47","tid":445832,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T18:38:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你budget 係幾多？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBudget 2000內<br />\n如果件羽絨本身話防風防水仲洗唔洗要多件gtx喺出面？</blockquote><br />\nMontbell 件1101502 防風但太薄 要加保暖內衣，但係夠輕好爽</blockquote><br />\n巴打有着過？<br />\n我就係貪佢夠輕 可以方便帶去旅行<br />\n保暖內衣有冇推薦？</blockquote><br />\n1101502 防風 外面唔需要再加gtx, 內衣odlo montbell ,odlo太厚 montbell 最厚羊毛比較貴</blockquote><br />\n雞仔嘜內衣巴打覺得點？</blockquote><br />\n未著過，話哂戶外界 好多有研究測試，功能性強好多，D人的去雪山都搵專業戶外牌子</blockquote><br />\nUNIQLO 最薄羽絨($299) + montbell 1128340 (有GTX) + 菊花牌短袖(啱啱好) / 雞仔嘜(行路會格勒底出汗)<br />\n北京 -5 度左右都冇問題."},{"pid":"fb321d1cc091bd4385e1a8261e173afdbd223ac4","tid":445832,"uid":80461,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T18:39:41.000Z","msg":"今年2月去完<br />\n我都係貪方便 帶兩件羽絨montbell+u記好薄+一件雞仔嗲+一件底衫+多件厚樓 都夠暖<br />\n可能我去岩果陣唔係好凍，同對上一年去差5,6度"},{"pid":"94fb66e3933be69a7f249a2218917e1409db18a0","tid":445832,"uid":11388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T18:40:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一月中去京都1000蚊budget買邊件好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無人推介下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我上年一月喺大阪同京都都係着啲劣劣地嘅淘寶羽絨<br />\n勉強夠暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上年一月我著Alpha Ma1 直頭熱（入面一件薄長袖）</blockquote><br />\n係真唔係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上年1月好似都長期10度以下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f1f86838c370c27ac6f5415861ca0bd74b442d","tid":445832,"uid":80461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T18:44:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一月中去京都1000蚊budget買邊件好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無人推介下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我上年一月喺大阪同京都都係着啲劣劣地嘅淘寶羽絨<br />\n勉強夠暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上年一月我著Alpha Ma1 直頭熱（入面一件薄長袖）</blockquote><br />\n係真唔係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上年1月好似都長期10度以下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n7-10度都好撚熱，1月頭係秋葉原行黎行去買下野係條街都已經熱到除淨件底衫+面衫就算"},{"pid":"41fc5a73c669c7126c9ada70bdf89369464926a4","tid":445832,"uid":51345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T19:12:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>要分清楚 Water repellent 定waterproof<br />\n防潑水同防水唔同</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來係咁<br />\n巴打有冇推介？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自己去落雪個d地方就著一件保暖打底衫<br />\n之後一件衛衣或者長䄂T<br />\n中層就著羽絨或者纖維褸<br />\n面頭再加件gtx<br />\n貪佢防風防水<br />\n如果就咁羽絨，因為會入風 所以硬係覺得無咁暖<br />\n<br />\n有時候去滑雪場因為大風雪所以有件防水褸都方便好多，個身一定唔會濕但如果你只係去啲會落少少雪嘅地方你防潑水都可以嘅，不過最好擔返把遮</blockquote><br />\n巴打講得好詳細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該晒你呀～"},{"pid":"40b774c12161839dbe2ddaea3d8222fd15a26ad4","tid":445832,"uid":51345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T19:13:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自己著開 AIGLE d打底衫 好掂<br />\n暖得黎又唔覺得焗身</blockquote><br />\n大約幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n大約500蚊一件，自己都著左7年</blockquote><br />\n咁耐用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正喎 抵着！<br />\n睇黎要搵日放假逐間逐間去睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acbf151eb9018323b8a33a69eca9222249868168","tid":445832,"uid":51345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T19:16:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2000內應該唔夠啦，直接買件gtx連內膽5千應該ok</blockquote><br />\n5000 overbudget咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAnyway唔該巴打～"},{"pid":"293a4a68b18006e2e07e1577284217b4e9350c2c","tid":445832,"uid":51345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T19:17:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>求其買件Montbell啦 再打下底<br />\n唔好企足幾個鐘街就乜都差唔多</blockquote><br />\n見啲人着過都話montbell唔錯～<br />\n咁褲呢？洗唔洗着條legging打底？定係加絨褲就夠？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n褲就一定要打底啦，唔洗講<br />\n同埋睇下你去邊啦最主要<br />\n行市內多既就著厚少少就ok la <br />\n第一次去我諗都唔會走得去邊啦，最多咪小樽左右</blockquote><br />\n會去小樽 同埋洞爺 登別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嗰頭會唔會凍啲？"},{"pid":"2dcfeeb8eecdbe49ac8cb6f54a94143fa780dd7e","tid":445832,"uid":51345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T19:18:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>columbia</blockquote><br />\n我見啲人話columbia唔保暖 巴打有冇着過？覺得點？</blockquote><br />\n兩件款外面gore tex入面羽絨銀底果種<br />\n其實都好暖<br />\n唔夠加多件super warm/雞仔嘜</blockquote><br />\n聽日去睇下先<br />\n唔該巴打～</blockquote><br />\n之前行山用過 4度 身夠暖 個頭就好凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做咩唔帶帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喺香港行？"},{"pid":"0b19e693d338b59708c9e40dfb2cf5bfc911d992","tid":445832,"uid":51345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T19:21:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBudget 2000內<br />\n如果件羽絨本身話防風防水仲洗唔洗要多件gtx喺出面？</blockquote><br />\nMontbell 件1101502 防風但太薄 要加保暖內衣，但係夠輕好爽</blockquote><br />\n巴打有着過？<br />\n我就係貪佢夠輕 可以方便帶去旅行<br />\n保暖內衣有冇推薦？</blockquote><br />\n1101502 防風 外面唔需要再加gtx, 內衣odlo montbell ,odlo太厚 montbell 最厚羊毛比較貴</blockquote><br />\n雞仔嘜內衣巴打覺得點？</blockquote><br />\n未著過，話哂戶外界 好多有研究測試，功能性強好多，D人的去雪山都搵專業戶外牌子</blockquote><br />\nUNIQLO 最薄羽絨($299) + montbell 1128340 (有GTX) + 菊花牌短袖(啱啱好) / 雞仔嘜(行路會格勒底出汗)<br />\n北京 -5 度左右都冇問題.</blockquote><br />\n1128340係男裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就算細碼我得150cm會唔會太大件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw冬天格甩底出汗特別臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adde4e565aa90625c7c9bc3556d0944a90a5b9f7","tid":445832,"uid":51345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T19:23:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今年2月去完<br />\n我都係貪方便 帶兩件羽絨montbell+u記好薄+一件雞仔嗲+一件底衫+多件厚樓 都夠暖<br />\n可能我去岩果陣唔係好凍，同對上一年去差5,6度</blockquote><br />\n差咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你着邊隻底衫？"},{"pid":"88f99ede404e9c0523122927d98584ce5b332cd1","tid":445832,"uid":77164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T21:49:48.000Z","msg":"上次著左件hoodie上雪山，唔死真係好好彩"},{"pid":"7d5d713668f647027cecd02fa2e94e7dee760144","tid":445832,"uid":51345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T00:03:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上次著左件hoodie上雪山，唔死真係好好彩</blockquote><br />\n巴打勇士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做咩咁搵命搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6993d55486147a5bfa31ff019f7d85f671e02a97","tid":445832,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T00:18:55.000Z","msg":"Superdry <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe8bbea7c9e082070847fd9b27cb2aac2b30127","tid":445832,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T00:21:46.000Z","msg":"superdry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d31df62dc1ffee84d6c4b5534a1da2b6c4fa65e","tid":445832,"uid":8253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T00:22:50.000Z","msg":"無錢就canda goose 加多少少上stone island<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e179e08b881ad5a1921b5168d518f03b0305bae2","tid":445832,"uid":1377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T00:28:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>superdry?唔記得呢篇新聞?<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0G-nagCxPvI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0G-nagCxPvI&d=emTNESBNAOyuGgpsxUMO7jOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=e885f54f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0G-nagCxPvI</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該係佢着錯衫姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你著superdry啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96d66dd15b2b86fb425c76457ea6659f3e76135","tid":445832,"uid":34080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T00:32:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ee01d14cc4f78548f38ebebeffa65fdabf711c6","tid":445832,"uid":47663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T00:36:29.000Z","msg":"我唔會著保暖衣，因為去到室內會熱到仆街，我會著quick dry 短袖衫，著中間一件保暖嘅褸，外加一件gtx 防水褸"},{"pid":"e03c3486616edc88a7bd6fe5437801db0f1e7950","tid":445832,"uid":5143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T00:43:40.000Z","msg":"我上年12月去北海道，無滑雪<br />\n都係著montbell，下身就打底褲+牛<br />\n想平可以去到日本先買(專門店/好日山莊)<br />\n平好多"},{"pid":"0a29d0d6094fc7ba965345f6ca281ed879517206","tid":445832,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T00:52:46.000Z","msg":"上年西班牙3度，未計風速減體溫<br />\n<br />\nPatagonia 低衫<br />\n長Tee<br />\nPatagonia R2<br />\nPatagonia nano air<br />\nArcteryx Gtx 防水褸<br />\n<br />\n由照出去到夜晚，照早同夜晚出去剛剛好，中午就中間個堆<br />\n<br />\nR2, 真係無買錯<br />\n<img src=\"https://shop.r10s.jp/auc-cliffside/cabinet/03991752/imgrc0071986661.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshop.r10s.jp%2Fauc-cliffside%2Fcabinet%2F03991752%2Fimgrc0071986661.jpg&h=f7a9d133&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12ce024b5fcc9843fe0ccb7ed1d7b6e122598554","tid":445832,"uid":3161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T01:00:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.mountainhardwear.com/mens-ghost-whisperer-down-hooded-jacket-1560921.html?cgid=awardWinners&amp;dwvar_1560921_variationColor=492#prefn1=genderGroup&amp;prefv1=Mens&amp;start=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mountainhardwear.com%2Fmens-ghost-whisperer-down-hooded-jacket-1560921.html%3Fcgid%3DawardWinners%26dwvar_1560921_variationColor%3D492%23prefn1%3DgenderGroup%26prefv1%3DMens%26start%3D0&d=emTNESBNAOyuGgpsxUMO7jOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=5e078641\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mountainhardwear.com/mens-ghost-whisperer-down-hooded-jacket-1560921.html?cgid=awardWinners&amp;dwvar_1560921_variationColor=492#prefn1=genderGroup&amp;prefv1=Mens&amp;start=0</a><br />\n<br />\n搭單問<br />\n呢件一月去北海道夠唔夠頂<br />\n打算heat tech 打底+呢件+風褸"},{"pid":"8adc112a3c1917f5b807e99887b24a133960625a","tid":445832,"uid":47663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T01:01:07.000Z","msg":"太子花園街排檔有平價打底褲賣，$100都唔洗就有一條，我買左一厚一薄，多數著薄嗰條，-30度我先會著厚嗰條"},{"pid":"6b34e5f0660e5e3b9d7bc3f7a56b3123bf8718c6","tid":445832,"uid":31198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T01:03:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>columbia</blockquote><br />\n我見啲人話columbia唔保暖 巴打有冇着過？覺得點？</blockquote><br />\n兩件款外面gore tex入面羽絨銀底果種<br />\n其實都好暖<br />\n唔夠加多件super warm/雞仔嘜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nYes 我二月去北海道就係著呢件野加heat tech都夠"},{"pid":"285ef51f35cf6916e010e18bce64ef2e67517bf5","tid":445832,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T01:07:26.000Z","msg":"要平既，去買件N3B，暖到出汗"},{"pid":"0e6a065adfa8d61a2a69486069150d74605c1cbb","tid":445832,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T01:08:48.000Z","msg":"比貴小小買 The North Face / Columbia 既二合一仲好。"},{"pid":"38e05f83434491dfeef33669ccec02a942ecb844","tid":445832,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T01:10:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>columbia</blockquote><br />\n我見啲人話columbia唔保暖 巴打有冇着過？覺得點？</blockquote><br />\n兩件款外面gore tex入面羽絨銀底果種<br />\n其實都好暖<br />\n唔夠加多件super warm/雞仔嘜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nYes 我二月去北海道就係著呢件野加heat tech都夠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前去北極都係呢種，入面簿長䄂都夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"936510c3ea9fe953d122eabb0bec9d28194b8b9f","tid":445832,"uid":10975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T01:11:03.000Z","msg":"北海道唔凍"},{"pid":"fa69df0d848a62b1d2e044fe40a4d4bd0c179ddf","tid":445832,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T01:29:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>北海道唔凍</blockquote><br />\n出現啦"},{"pid":"c7c7ffab018ca0850de2cec8e9b0318647255471","tid":445832,"uid":117304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T06:33:33.000Z","msg":"其實如果面果件防水+薄薄地既gtx/定係厚厚地但唔防水既非GTX好？<br />\n假設我入面係薄羽絨加打底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d849d79512cd309d0037169a34105671d196c8b2","tid":445832,"uid":144275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T06:39:14.000Z","msg":"著件廢既羽絨去<br />\n去到札幌先買件加拿大鵝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本d真羽絨平到你唔信<br />\n有牌子無牌子都平過係香港買"},{"pid":"0ac4b4a246cd77725f8d256286ce690a8b59d1b8","tid":445832,"uid":24635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T06:43:33.000Z","msg":"之前買件bigpack都夠做"},{"pid":"6c92e5678496c8ffeefd51b2e3eb9cd44c309811","tid":445832,"uid":128100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T08:31:35.000Z","msg":"買Canada goose 啦"},{"pid":"cf081486f8fdac107b74a5ba0971b7acb9f8087c","tid":445832,"uid":23315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T08:51:28.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"b6845903eb1d6e27445f8d0efc337561a2f27395","tid":445832,"uid":51345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:46:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Superdry <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你就比膠 下面就比gd <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4236ce90885d552ee8702b0eb2fcdee45a362a7","tid":445832,"uid":51345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:50:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無錢就canda goose 加多少少上stone island<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nCanada goose啲款都幾靚"},{"pid":"7a92aec4c11e1fc6580268c9d0348f1aa1ef9e15","tid":445832,"uid":51345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:53:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我上年12月去北海道，無滑雪<br />\n都係著montbell，下身就打底褲+牛<br />\n想平可以去到日本先買(專門店/好日山莊)<br />\n平好多</blockquote><br />\n日本真係好平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但我依家件羽絨厚到仆街 唔想帶過去再喺日本買"},{"pid":"78d3d8bca582e7bd3aeed3d656e94a16a99196ca","tid":445832,"uid":51345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>太子花園街排檔有平價打底褲賣，$100都唔洗就有一條，我買左一厚一薄，多數著薄嗰條，-30度我先會著厚嗰條</blockquote><br />\n我本身仲諗住淘架添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"334c19070a6358b89d10e6efbec68894b0302f84","tid":445832,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T11:17:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>太子花園街排檔有平價打底褲賣，$100都唔洗就有一條，我買左一厚一薄，多數著薄嗰條，-30度我先會著厚嗰條</blockquote><br />\n我本身仲諗住淘架添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n貼身野就唔好淘啦"},{"pid":"88ae00ec63573cb404fade5c2837e714e0f274c0","tid":445832,"uid":10975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T15:37:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>北海道唔凍</blockquote><br />\n出現啦</blockquote><br />\n真係唔算凍<br />\n啲人又話雪褲雪鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e0aee9d8a78b3fc204367ddbb5045291b4f9ab4","tid":445832,"uid":144275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T15:47:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>北海道唔凍</blockquote><br />\n出現啦</blockquote><br />\n真係唔算凍<br />\n啲人又話雪褲雪鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要視乎冬天去北海道邊度<br />\n層雲峽冰瀑祭既話呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n層雲峽係我人生第一次感受到凍到個鼻同耳仔甩係咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0970293f25384d96f1f66bab9d15ebae5a4c87c","tid":445832,"uid":10975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T16:08:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>北海道唔凍</blockquote><br />\n出現啦</blockquote><br />\n真係唔算凍<br />\n啲人又話雪褲雪鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要視乎冬天去北海道邊度<br />\n層雲峽冰瀑祭既話呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n層雲峽係我人生第一次感受到凍到個鼻同耳仔甩係咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSorry 冬天冇辦法去呢到<br />\n只係去函館 札榥 美瑛"},{"pid":"b9b452fa67798a439b5e811bf57e1ce75f160ef4","tid":445832,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T19:28:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBudget 2000內<br />\n如果件羽絨本身話防風防水仲洗唔洗要多件gtx喺出面？</blockquote><br />\nMontbell 件1101502 防風但太薄 要加保暖內衣，但係夠輕好爽</blockquote><br />\n巴打有着過？<br />\n我就係貪佢夠輕 可以方便帶去旅行<br />\n保暖內衣有冇推薦？</blockquote><br />\n1101502 防風 外面唔需要再加gtx, 內衣odlo montbell ,odlo太厚 montbell 最厚羊毛比較貴</blockquote><br />\n雞仔嘜內衣巴打覺得點？</blockquote><br />\n未著過，話哂戶外界 好多有研究測試，功能性強好多，D人的去雪山都搵專業戶外牌子</blockquote><br />\nUNIQLO 最薄羽絨($299) + montbell 1128340 (有GTX) + 菊花牌短袖(啱啱好) / 雞仔嘜(行路會格勒底出汗)<br />\n北京 -5 度左右都冇問題.</blockquote><br />\n1128340係男裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就算細碼我得150cm會唔會太大件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw冬天格甩底出汗特別臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有女裝架嘛. 可以買1128533, 1128542, 1128341, 1128578 .日本買平好多."},{"pid":"81d7774cb5add70bf79de03659f698aaaf7ccb40","tid":445832,"uid":10035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:26:18.000Z","msg":"曾經信過高登仔成日話香港濕凍=外國零度咁上下（未出過國） <br />\n早幾年一月份去左北海道只係著多左件衫 凍撚到爭d暈低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bcd29162d9a4c4e00abf054c3ddc1529094deb4","tid":445832,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:33:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曾經信過高登仔成日話香港濕凍=外國零度咁上下（未出過國） <br />\n早幾年一月份去左北海道只係著多左件衫 凍撚到爭d暈低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n濕凍係凍啲姐，零度又誇咗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf4f8f13035cdee6ebaa9a5c55059fcb81d0a41","tid":445832,"uid":72312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T07:24:29.000Z","msg":"搭單問，​#​1102432同​#1102463，呢兩件其實有咩分別？香港邊度買Montbell平啲？Overlander見到有#1102463，但無#​1102432，未見過實物唔係好敢上網買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3acd8d726acdd06316248e8d6f7ccb1a5e592aa","tid":445832,"uid":87123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T10:38:13.000Z","msg":"The north face得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f395ebac21bd9fd0f433daf9b2adbd3bbfb663d","tid":445832,"uid":14548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T10:48:59.000Z","msg":"12月尾去大阪京都，就咁一件羽絨夠唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？應該唔會低過零度？"},{"pid":"b37d00140b6c889d7dfe60b0951839bc86385476","tid":445832,"uid":10975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T10:51:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>The north face得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇問題啦<br />\n我都係著tnf goretex面<br />\n入面仲有件長袖絨毛可以除<br />\n熱到出汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6aeb632c7bcab9c1645ccb54f9f21d7e25f12b9","tid":445832,"uid":81756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T10:56:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曾經信過高登仔成日話香港濕凍=外國零度咁上下（未出過國） <br />\n早幾年一月份去左北海道只係著多左件衫 凍撚到爭d暈低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心香港冬天幾度凍過溫哥華負10度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa9e723ee7633f4edee406284ee3184563c944fc","tid":445832,"uid":81270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T10:57:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>superdry?唔記得呢篇新聞?<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0G-nagCxPvI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0G-nagCxPvI&d=emTNESBNAOyuGgpsxUMO7jOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=e885f54f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0G-nagCxPvI</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該係佢着錯衫姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSuperdry 根本就唔暖，係for 英國嘅濕凍天氣，大概-5~10 度； 屌你，北海道可以負廿幾三十度。你咪唔好信囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acac7c00897094abd8fd0dbfc088e2e5ad0cfaa6","tid":445832,"uid":23315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T11:18:33.000Z","msg":"係日本amazon買mont bell好似幾抵"},{"pid":"c0f908e3f895321a1866e891464d62b38159e4b9","tid":445832,"uid":81756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T11:45:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係日本amazon買mont bell好似幾抵</blockquote><br />\n係香港乜都賣得零舍貴過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1176a16c6d4bbc00c23a653a793d286b6bc6dcc","tid":445832,"uid":48211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:21:15.000Z","msg":"我自己覺得如果唔怕凍嘅話<br />\n底衫 T恤 fleece 風䄛<br />\n1-3度左右頂到<br />\n想再暖啲fleece轉羽絨<br />\n都好夠下"},{"pid":"e349845746c378df2ed533d8489eefe690ef162c","tid":445832,"uid":34534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:30:34.000Z","msg":"識著緊係成身潮牌啦理得佢凍唔凍啫<br />\n連登仔女驚咩鬼野凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用下腦都知d潮牌得個樣架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上面貼埋新聞比你睇<br />\n你都可以話係佢著錯衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等睇你著superdry上新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125687b988892626ed17a28cc72dba9b6bdc7efa","tid":445832,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T14:10:26.000Z","msg":"唔怕凍既人，我建議佢地著U 記就算<br />\n<br />\nps. 有咩事都唔好入我數"},{"pid":"3f87aa194e3858c4249e82959cfc252293eb7af6","tid":445832,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:11:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔怕凍既人，我建議佢地著U 記就算<br />\n<br />\nps. 有咩事都唔好入我數</blockquote><br />\n我覺得U記夠暖。又平。每2年買1次新。<br />\n幾千銀，1年著得2，3次。<br />\n次次去旅行影親都係嗰件羽絨<br />\n我認係我窮。唔捨得年年使幾千銀買件新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76af0cdf728839096026f962293e5d1e07ce31ee","tid":445832,"uid":8601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:13:49.000Z","msg":"如果想保暖嘅千祈千祈唔好買superdry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9058835c85afeb8c146ad9b7c281bc60be1c51c9","tid":445832,"uid":59130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T11:03:57.000Z","msg":"搭單問埋想買件防水既卡奇mountain parka ,想係香港都著到，causal 少少既，唔介意入面著多幾件衫<br />\n除左呢件patagonia 既torrentshell parka(229usd) 外，有無其他選擇<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/190353_5080e68ff9aaf7e8fec848192b6805a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F190353_5080e68ff9aaf7e8fec848192b6805a2.jpg&h=f9672422&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5db43d8ee92b84066b24ce9ff6dd074fee36f23a","tid":445832,"uid":59130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T15:48:16.000Z","msg":"無人冬天去旅行？？"},{"pid":"10d889ed8ffb97a1c8b1fa544dc5a9018ea264bf","tid":445832,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T15:55:20.000Z","msg":"superdry呢啲on9 brand款又唔靚，又冇function仲要賣到貴一貴，憑咩？"},{"pid":"4170fdce9b9e0996a50d8f61dc7dd042d332ed7c","tid":445832,"uid":96417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T17:09:15.000Z","msg":"1月去芬蘭 仲未諗到買咩既上身 保暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd88491969098a901c75d7af17fb8da61626142","tid":445832,"uid":57439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T18:27:53.000Z","msg":"睇樓主出門先諗住買羽絨, 應該都唔太怕凍<br />\n<br />\n如果唔滑雪, 日程都未必太多戶外<br />\n<br />\n上年1月去北海道(札幌, 登別 函館), 一件zara抓毛底parka 就夠, 淨係旭川好凍, 加多件u 記299羽絨背心<br />\n<br />\n反而褲就真係買左條heat tech, 咪諗住牛仔褲, 入風好凍<br />\n<br />\n厚底boots, 頸巾同手套就is a must"},{"pid":"b2381ecd391aed567f29e94ce9f790cde0be8538","tid":445832,"uid":66740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T18:30:11.000Z","msg":"Mont Bell sure, superdry垃撚垃"},{"pid":"c679db3d384d11e80494ed7293396f492bd2c8c4","tid":445832,"uid":99582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T18:37:11.000Z","msg":"我係東京街頭 0度 就咁著左件b皮褸加短tee 凍到閪咁<br />\n<br />\n仲要行返去酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de071be98505a7a79cd8deb446e0765589f48999","tid":445832,"uid":144534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T18:46:23.000Z","msg":"其實真心Moncler雖然貴 但真心好暖<br />\n平日係London 加件tee頂得住冬天"},{"pid":"953d01f4fee45e92b395285d88376290199749f2","tid":445832,"uid":38440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T18:54:21.000Z","msg":"仲以為加拿大鵝唔ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e96e8337cef2156e5801098fa37b2cbafc90f4e","tid":445832,"uid":155088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T00:25:41.000Z","msg":"睇樓主都係鍾意潮牌多啲，買superdry啦，去到頂唔順係日本montbell再買囉，又平啲。我聖誕去東北，我就帶齊羽絨，防水褸同褲，雪靴同防水鞋，有備無患。我覺得鞋都好緊要，試過對鞋入水凍到腳趾都feel唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d7d7d41506ceff071c3d4ff33