":32390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T05:52:51.000Z","msg":"U記嗰件899女裝羽絨夠唔夠<br />\n1月去北海道 我女友買咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f117a64fbb8fc68daa3f611a487ae4a9005f99","tid":445832,"uid":155088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T06:52:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>U記嗰件899女裝羽絨夠唔夠<br />\n1月去北海道 我女友買咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n件衫防唔防風？唔防嘅就配多件防風褸，唔係嘅啲風吹入去，點都唔會暖。"},{"pid":"575d0268b1bcbff8b7f392a3aa855d6f073c68e1","tid":445832,"uid":70817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T14:13:38.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"f1e34487bee708f34f4eb2afdb2ad29918d800c6","tid":445832,"uid":36415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T15:14:35.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"e6e1fe08bfcf41454edcbb7d1fa7202e31a0817a","tid":445832,"uid":80633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T15:27:36.000Z","msg":"superdry不如唔好買<br />\n又唔係專門保暖"},{"pid":"7af4c21d35e419b3af1fcb9b5e6b1797d7133acf","tid":445832,"uid":20990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T15:41:25.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"4c7f560bf4be195fd7440daa54b741787b3d086c","tid":445832,"uid":65406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T15:46:39.000Z","msg":"鞋可噴定防水層,<br />\n試過我對唔防水,但噴左野既行山鞋踩中水坑,<br />\n好彩水深淺過鞋桶,如果唔係食得屎"},{"pid":"29985bc39845940c5a18869a4fcacd794782d527","tid":445832,"uid":12426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T15:50:49.000Z","msg":"仲未有canada goose?"},{"pid":"1fbfd94bf7f96925361eff2294795faf43afdbd7","tid":445832,"uid":20990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T16:37:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲未有canada goose?</blockquote><br />\n上邊有講，不過價錢太貴"},{"pid":"d2fab8ad39a7c19eccf85bf7537fdf963955a75c","tid":445832,"uid":59130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T13:45:52.000Z","msg":"一月北海道會唔會凍到要著雪褲"},{"pid":"3e5c85f62fd8ee031b9dfaa0a4dd8237b6c83281","tid":445832,"uid":116774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T14:48:48.000Z","msg":"咁 Columbia 或者 northface 呢？"},{"pid":"00ff4b95e23fb4d9dcd43eaf1b571b1c656f2885","tid":445832,"uid":3436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T16:35:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>北海道唔凍</blockquote><br />\n出現啦</blockquote><br />\n真係唔算凍<br />\n啲人又話雪褲雪鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要視乎冬天去北海道邊度<br />\n層雲峽冰瀑祭既話呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n層雲峽係我人生第一次感受到凍到個鼻同耳仔甩係咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係凍既 但無咁誇張 可能果晚無咩風 同埋其實個場唔係話好大 酒店食飽出發 行完返酒店其實都係一粒鐘搞掂<br />\n去旭川動物園果陣先係最難頂 有少少太陽都好 D風吹埋黎 goretex都無用 除非包實塊面"},{"pid":"f610a6fbb09f1ac60e533db60d316b77de4f5f11","tid":445832,"uid":3436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T16:37:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一月北海道會唔會凍到要著雪褲</blockquote><br />\n其實最緊要係對鞋同襪<br />\n衫褲可以著好多件<br />\n但鞋同襪只有一對<br />\n同埋一旦踩深雪/日頭D雪溶溶地 對鞋又唔防水 襪又唔保暖就仆街了"}]}